s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f69b74042b5a22e9c854b8299143268cc9cd4c4","tid":90644,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:22:56.000Z","msg":"月經post <br />\n搵滅蟲公司搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3784a36437accb57dcb80341f0a1fbc15eb4e6f8","tid":90644,"uid":61991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"床蝨黎架，我之前試過一次，愈生愈多，全屋人奶晒野，咬撚左成幾個月，最後搵人黎搞得掂。真心建議你快d搵人清，否則會愈生愈多，到時仲難清"},{"pid":"aedbdc1878726ccf41bb6f349b92aec359cf7d3d","tid":90644,"uid":55575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:25:50.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"66edf1cd22be3eb9d32706b7305cd2e06d5a08a1","tid":90644,"uid":55575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"仲要咁撚大隻<br />\n樓主住邊？"},{"pid":"4442a5dfeeab163d694c397dd4d617f646d9caa8","tid":90644,"uid":36952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"最好搵滅蟲公司做<br />\n同埋係比貴少少搵間包滅既做<br />\n咩叫包滅？完成後1個月內有事會再上黎/退錢（前者好d)<br />\n<br />\n通常佢地既方法係：<br />\n1. 用藥（幫到大約3成）<br />\n2. 用蒸氣熱所有傢私床鋪（大約3成）<br />\n3. 叫你拎曬d野去處理（3成）<br />\n4. DE粉/藥粉<br />\n<br />\n先講用藥：主要係噴，焗係係用<br />\n因為氣咪對佢地影響唔大<br />\n床蝨主要靠你體溫/呼出既二氧化碳搵到你<br />\n用完藥佢地經過會中毒自己慢慢死<br />\n煙霧彈：無用，因為係針對跳蚤<br />\n讀音相同但字唔同，所以好多人誤會<br />\n<br />\n蒸氣：任何insects 高過5/60度都會死，所以高溫殺係有用，但同用藥一樣，要對準位先得<br />\n<br />\n拎曬所有野處理，包括傢私，衣物<br />\n通常叫你掉得就掉<br />\n因為床蝨鐘意係近人既地方吸血，方便搵食<br />\n尤其床，sofa, pillows,被<br />\n前者好大機會要拆床搞，尤其木床，因爲床蝨好鐘意躲在木傢私，所以好多人叫佢地木蝨<br />\n<br />\n至於床，如果有透仔孔（側面）<br />\n佢地好大機會入左床<br />\n所以通常都要掉<br />\n就算張床係幾皮買番黎都係<br />\n<br />\n衣物，洗完入真空袋，留幾件替換<br />\n點洗？拎完去乾衣鋪/自己用高於60度既洗，但件衫質地有機會變<br />\n<br />\n粉：用藥道理一樣，願者上吊"},{"pid":"f21f95bc0b25027a47d683b5bcad939695b168a1","tid":90644,"uid":9648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"仆得街，你d親戚去你度拜年/你去人地度拜年都會惹畀人，送大禮今次真係"},{"pid":"6d12f3b5bed448a73649443635cf97ce1980c17d","tid":90644,"uid":36952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用煙霧彈焗有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕對無用<br />\n反而會搞到佢地走去其他位/喱得更埋"},{"pid":"c28eb81871aef8e8f4eca33a229ba1ba3d225135","tid":90644,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"樓主住咩地方？劏房？"},{"pid":"2a933589b4a191b96ccf2aafe05ca2ce28e61579","tid":90644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月經post <br />\n搵滅蟲公司搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問邊間滅蟲公司信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0550f38982f8a89c4d0bdfcd599cb2940f5c1b0","tid":90644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆得街，你d親戚去你度拜年/你去人地度拜年都會惹畀人，送大禮今次真係</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0390161f851bedb1f1ae3685b055f85db134cac4","tid":90644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score