017-01-23T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/59f301a3c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2F59f301a3c5.jpg&h=d3baab38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老母唔知係邊搵到呢件嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚準備同木蝨死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8b9fc7ee5e3ef630038dd3468e1937db3217c5","tid":90644,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"大隻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d332a56f39bb5979ad805f76b6e0a7e587824473","tid":90644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大隻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f2f6313e1b73e2e53243ad77d66a004fb7d77d","tid":90644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/5d981d53c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2F5d981d53c3.png&h=8d5b66e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我阿媽d fd送嘅  唔知用唔用好？<br />\n<br />\n大陸農藥好似好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98158179150f4a58d9f63f0a6f424a3e073e6e70","tid":90644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"【本報綜合外電報導】臭蟲再次大舉侵襲全美，屋主和寓公用盡各種方法，希望消除這種頑固的吸血蟲，有些人因而仰賴危險的戶外用殺蟲劑以及唯利是圖的除蟲公司。<br />\n<br />\n由於問題嚴重，美國環境保護署（EPA）本月曾警告，不要將戶外用殺蟲劑用於室內。EPA同時警告，有愈來愈多除蟲公司和其他相關行業，作出「保證有效或價錢低廉」等不實承諾。<br />\n<br />\n此番臭蟲肆虐美國家庭的嚴重程度，是逾半世紀以來僅見，且大多對一般殺蟲劑都有抵抗力。因此造成若干家庭和除蟲公司改用更危險化學殺蟲劑，可能會傷害中樞神經系統、造成皮膚和眼睛不適，甚至引發癌症。<br />\n<br />\n竭力防治境內臭蟲肆虐的俄亥俄州當局，已請求EPA同意在室內使用「殘殺威」（propoxur）殺蟲劑。EPA認為殘殺威可能致癌，已於二○○七年禁止室內使用。但目前約有另外二十五州，支持俄亥俄州的緊急豁免請求。<br />\n<br />\nEPA發言人表示，該署曾於六月駁回這項請求，並答應將會找出新穎有效的化學殺蟲劑，殺死那些會造成皮膚發癢、紅腫、抓破後易引發傷口感染的臭蟲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.merit-times.com.tw/NewsPage.aspx?unid=200852\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.merit-times.com.tw%2FNewsPage.aspx%3Funid%3D200852&d=LeNpBdcj6I5QCBKhB5VE%2BQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f7143518\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.merit-times.com.tw/NewsPage.aspx?unid=200852</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92ddce25a7c94e57d546e32b40128cd2385e244","tid":90644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65145c484a4ef5e2d4f5e0ec4b1bc5a9076fdea","tid":90644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:08:31.000Z","msg":"好毒 頭有d暈"}]}